margin: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder;\">注意：若点击下载按钮无法下载小程序前端，请检查是否弹出窗口被浏览器拦截！</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder;\">工具上传视频教程：</span><a href=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMzY5MzU3NzM3Mg==.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\">http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMzY5MzU3NzM3Mg==.html</a><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder;\">注意：使用工具上传时，项目目录一定不能出错，项目目录下面必须包含app.js、app.json，app.wxss这些文件</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/1738d500a5670460b8f032a30c204f96_1252x514.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><hr style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; overflow: visible; border-top: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><h1 data-line=\"21\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 2.25em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2; min-height: 1rem;\"><a id=\"_21\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>小程序提交审核</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">请登录微信公众平台：<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/</a><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">进入“开发管理”菜单，找到刚才上传的开发版，即可提交审核<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/0954be748effaa89a9cb431edd144477_732x506.png\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder;\">提交审核的时候，可添加”pages/index/index”也就是首页为功能页面<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">标题，标签需要跟你的小程序或者卖的东西相关<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">服务类目，必须是你卖的东西所对应的类目</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/53788b515bc322b6998a130ad2db6b0d_718x505.png\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><hr style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; overflow: visible; border-top: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder;\">注意：审核期间，建议关闭分销，商家入驻和裂变红包</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">分销功能关闭：分销中心-&gt;分销设置-&gt;基础设置 分销层级：不开启<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">或者商城管理-&gt;小程序设置-&gt;个人中心 菜单栏：把分销中心去掉<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">裂变红包关闭：应用专区-&gt;裂变拆红包-&gt;红包设置 开启活动:关闭<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">商家入驻关闭：商城管理-&gt;小程序设置-&gt;首页布局 删除（没添加则无需操作）“好店推荐”模块<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">商城管理-&gt;小程序设置-&gt;个人中心 菜单栏：把入驻商去掉</p><hr style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; overflow: visible; border-top: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><hr style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; overflow: visible; border-top: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><h1 data-line=\"49\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 2.25em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2; min-height: 1rem;\"><a id=\"_49\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>小程序发布</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">请登录微信公众平台：<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/</a><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">小程序审核通后，腾讯会发通知给你，你就可以发布小程序了。如下图：<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/bce1f219a7c7f7024bc5f86515f53004_722x292.png\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p></div>', 'normal', 1535693539, 1535693539);
