ap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"1_1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>1.订单基本信息</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">购买时候选择了快递方式的订单在该页面中展示（具体在商城管理-系统设置-商城设置中设置）<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/858b03d4601384894feedd3821027201_1773x890.png\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><h3 data-line=\"5\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.43; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.5em;\"><a id=\"__5\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>注：全部不包含已取消订单， 首页显示的订单数就是全部里面的订单数</h3><h2 data-line=\"7\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"2_7\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>2.订单操作基本信息</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">1.未付款订单：能够修改价格，未付款订单超时将自动取消，时间设置在商城管理-系统设置-商城设置中设置<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/6b5834c40b36337092650143e44353ca_462x216.png\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">2.待发货订单：待发货是已付款的订单，支持发货功能，发货可以填写快递跟物流单号（商城管理-系统设置-商城设置-快递鸟），也可以使用电子面单功能（商城管理-系统设置-快递单打印），也可以无需物流，并填写商家留言，用户可在小程序端看到</p><h3 data-line=\"12\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.43; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.5em;\"><a id=\"_12\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>注:电子面单请咨询当地快递公司或者快递公司总部，其中邮政的电子面单必须用到邮政编码，其他快递邮编可不填</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/acfa949658d679c6f1b148e17c684c66_413x502.png\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><h3 data-line=\"14\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.43; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.5em;\"><a id=\"_14\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>用户若已付款未发货可申请取消，需要管理员审核，审核通过金额原路返回</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/23c786e9a5020bf8659fa0085f12b15b_460x141.png\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">3.待收货订单：用户在小程序段可点击收货，若用户长时间没有收货，系统会根据商城管理-商城设置中的自动收货时间自动收货，收货之后，若该订单没有超过系统规定的售后时间（商城管理-系统设置-商城设置中的售后时间），用户也可以申请退货，订单进入售后订单处理；<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">4.已完成：订单超过售后时间且无取消退货，则为已完成订单<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">5.已取消：未付款自动取消或者已付款未发货取消的订单列表</p></div>', 'normal', 1535694107, 1535694107);
