t; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">用户管理模块主要是管理小程序的所有用户，包含对所有用户的数据统计，包括订单数，优惠券数量，卡券数量，积分<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">另外可以设置会员等级，充值积分、充值余额，设置核销员等<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/03669b59bbd76e63a33a691d367e4dff_1339x371.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><h1 data-line=\"6\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 2.25em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2; min-height: 1rem;\"><a id=\"_6\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>用户列表</h1><h2 data-line=\"7\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"1_7\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>1.用户基本信息</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">点击用户列表，查看用户基本信息：头像，昵称，加入时间，身份（会员等级），订单数，优惠券数量，卡券数量，当前积分，当前余额<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">并且能够点击跳转，查看具体的订单，优惠券等情况；</p><h2 data-line=\"11\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"2_11\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>2.操作</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">编辑：修改会员等级，可修改该用户到指定会员等级<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">充值积分：可充值/扣除会员积分（会员积分用于抵扣金额，在商城管理-系统设置-商城设置中设置比例）<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">充值余额：可充值/扣除会员余额（会员余额充值功能请在“营销管理-&gt;充值”菜单进行设置或者添加充值方案）</p></div>', 'normal', 1535694258, 1535694258);
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (69, 67, 'two', '核销员', '<div class=\"article-head\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; position: relative; padding: 10px 20px; height: 50px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 20px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 200px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; min-height: 1rem; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(126, 136, 139);\">核销员</h1></div><div class=\"article-body\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 980px; padding: 9px 24px; line-height: 1.7em; font-size: 1.14em; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><h1 data-line=\"0\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 2.25em; margin-bottom: 14px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2; min-height: 1rem; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><a id=\"_0\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>核销员管理</h1><h2 data-line=\"1\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"1_1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>1.添加核销员</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/1347c6325ce6e72aee53b893dfda7639_1120x550.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">注：添加核销员之前请先进入\"内容管理-门店\"添加好门店，具体请查看\"内容管理-门店\"菜单</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">核销员使用微信昵称查找，注：必须是进入过小程序并且授权登陆过有记录的用户才能查找到</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">添加之后该核销员能够核销跟商城有关的所有核销码，包括商城订单，拼团订单，预约订单，卡券</li></ul><h3 data-line=\"8\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.43; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.5em;\"><a id=\"_8\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>注：使用微信自带的扫一扫即可核销</h3><h2 data-line=\"9\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"2_9\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>2.操作</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">对已有核销员，可以解除核销员资格，也可以修改核销员所属门店</p><h3 data-line=\"11\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.43; margin: 0px; font-size: 1.5em;\"><a id=\"_11\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>注：门店目前是用于展示跟统计核销订单跟卡券的作用，并不是多商户，也没有门店后台</h3></div><div class=\"article-navigation\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 980px; position: relative; padding: 9px 24px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"></div>', 'normal', 1535694280, 1535694280);
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (70, 67, 'two', '会员等级', '<div class=\"article-head\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; position: relative; padding: 10px 20px; height: 50px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 20px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 200px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; min-height: 1rem; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(126, 136, 139);\">会员等级</h1></div><div class=\"article-body\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 980px; padding: 9px 24px; line-height: 1.7em; font-size: 1.14em; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><h1 data-line=\"0\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 2.25em; margin-bottom: 14px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2; min-height: 1rem; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><a id=\"_0\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>会员等级管理</h1><h2 data-line=\"1\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"1_1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>1.添加会员等级</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/12dc56d108125023106034bc3ffddb0e_930x547.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">目前会员能够最多添加100级，会员等级越高，享受的权益越多，<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">升级条件：累计完成订单金额，该金额必须是会员下单收货并且过了售后时间之后才计算入内<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">折扣：支持0.1-10 10就是不打折，若填写8.5 就是全场商品享受8.5折</p><h2 data-line=\"10\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"2_10\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>2.会员等级说明</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">会员等级说明：在小程序端会员中心显示的文字性描述<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/99b674a99b41cdb6b08b36815ad58d0f_1005x441.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><h2 data-line=\"15\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"3_15\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>3.设置会员购买</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/cb83901e8ca45f7450f3b77cc40060b8_1011x564.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">当设置购买价格不为0 则默认开启会员购买<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">用户在个人中心点击头像旁会员图标进入会员中心，<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">根据设置购买成为会员<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">所有购买记录会在“用户管理-&gt;会员购买记录”中展示</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">**注：会员购买不计算分销。购买成功无法退款，购买之后则成为对应会员，享受会员折扣<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">**</p></div>', 'normal', 1535694306, 1535694306);
