nt; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">有了分销商之后，分销商通过转发，推广海报推广小程序，当他们的下线产生交易额的时候，就会产生佣金，这些订单为分销订单，在该页面显示 ；<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">分销订单管理显示所有分销订单信息，包括订单基本信息， 以及分销商佣金信息，可根据订单号或者下单用户搜索</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/40c1c59f7e18bb18a94385a7fd1e605b_1184x575.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p></div>', 'normal', 1535694427, 1535694427);
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (76, 73, 'two', '分销提现', '<div class=\"article-head\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; position: relative; padding: 10px 20px; height: 50px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 20px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 200px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; min-height: 1rem; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(126, 136, 139);\">分销提现</h1></div><div class=\"article-body\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 980px; padding: 9px 24px; line-height: 1.7em; font-size: 1.14em; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><h1 data-line=\"0\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 2.25em; margin-bottom: 14px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2; min-height: 1rem; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><a id=\"_0\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>提现管理</h1><h2 data-line=\"1\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"1_1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>1.进入提现管理：</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">当分销商的佣金达到一定程度，可申请提现（注：可提现佣金必须是订单已完成-收货并且已过售后时间）<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/b47a04ba7d776432aa325cc42fde5beb_932x206.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><h2 data-line=\"7\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"2_7\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>2.提现打款：</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/13d9a8cae1efb91964aa6c9c20c96419_938x225.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">打款分为自动跟手动<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">1.自动，用户申请提现到微信，<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder;\">店家需开通微信支付企业付款到零钱功能</span>，具体请参考《小程序常用设置及参数获取》章节<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">2.手动，根据分销商填写的微信账号/支付宝账号/银行卡号 线下打款，打款后直接点击手动打款完成。</p><h2 data-line=\"14\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"3_14\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>3.如何开通“微信支付企业付款到零钱”功能</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">请参考《小程序常用设置及参数获取》章节<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><a href=\"https://www.kancloud.cn/justdoit2018/xcx/583338#6_50\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\">https://www.kancloud.cn/justdoit2018/xcx/583338#6_50</a><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">或许以下链接<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><a href=\"https://pay.weixin.qq.com/wiki/doc/api/tools/mch_pay.php?chapter=14_1\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\">https://pay.weixin.qq.com/wiki/doc/api/tools/mch_pay.php?chapter=14_1</a></p></div>', 'normal', 1535694452, 1535694452);
