t; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/6045ca9849a60c8673c3a87bf0b71afb_994x354.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><h4 data-line=\"3\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.7em; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.25em;\"><a id=\"_3\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>设置分销等级自定义名称</h4><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">根据基础设置里面设置的分销层级，在该页面中可以自定义设置全局分销商等级名称，也可以使用默认名称；</p><h4 data-line=\"6\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.7em; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.25em;\"><a id=\"_6\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>支持百分比和固定金额设置</h4><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">1-百分比是根据商品实际支付金额计算；<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">分销佣金举例说明：A，B, C, D 四个用户， A，B，C都是分销商， B是A的下级，C是B的下级，D是C的下级，若佣金设置1级10%，2级5%，3级3%，D消费了100元，则C获得佣金10元，B获得佣金5元，A获得佣金3元<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">2-固定金额根据商品件数来计算：<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">分销佣金举例说明：A，B, C, D 四个用户， A，B，C都是分销商， B是A的下级，C是B的下级，D是C的下级，若佣金设置1级10元，2级5元，3级3元，D消费购买了2件商品，则C获得佣金20元，B获得佣金10元，A获得佣金6元，若D购买了1件商品，则C获得佣金10元，B获得佣金5元，A获得佣金3元</p><h4 data-line=\"11\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.7em; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.25em;\"><a id=\"_11\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>注：该设置是全局设置，若在单商品中设置了商品各自的佣金规则，则以单商品佣金设置为准</h4><h1 data-line=\"14\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 2.25em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2; min-height: 1rem;\"><a id=\"_14\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>自购佣金设置：</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder;\">自购佣金只有在基础设置中开启了“分销内购”才有效<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">若开启了3级佣金，并且开启了“分销内购”<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">分销商自己购买商品，享受一级佣金，上级享受二级佣金，上上级享受三级佣金。</span></p></div>', 'normal', 1535694531, 1535694531);
