nsparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">如下图，可以修改分销中心文字表述。<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/e17c723d825b34dedb8f47b2a2649380_1023x677.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p></div>', 'normal', 1535694556, 1535694556);
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (81, 73, 'two', '小程序前端分销中心说明', '<div class=\"article-head\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; position: relative; padding: 10px 20px; height: 50px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><h1 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 20px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 200px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; min-height: 1rem; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(126, 136, 139);\">小程序前端分销中心说明</h1></div><div class=\"article-body\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: 980px; padding: 9px 24px; line-height: 1.7em; font-size: 1.14em; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\"><h1 data-line=\"0\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 2.25em; margin-bottom: 14px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2; min-height: 1rem; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><a id=\"_0\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>前端分销中心页面效果图如下</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/93cc9f32dee9ee82c83a45a8f595b43e_404x712.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><h2 data-line=\"5\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"1_5\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>1.提现跟分销佣金：</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">点击查看分销商个人分销佣金情况，可申请提现 （注：只有下级的订单已收货且过了售后时间才计算入内）</p><h2 data-line=\"8\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"2_8\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>2.分销订单：</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">点击查看下级的订单情况** (注：改处显示所有订单，包括未完成，已完成，未过售后，已过售后时间的订单，因此金额会跟分销佣金显示不匹配)**</p><h2 data-line=\"11\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"3_11\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>3.提现明细：</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">点击查看个人提现记录</p><h2 data-line=\"14\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"4_14\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>4.我的团队：</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">点击查看分销商所属下级成员，并且显示该成员订单数**（已完成过售后订单）**</p><h2 data-line=\"17\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family