。</p><h2 data-line=\"4\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"_4\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>商户列表</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">商户列表，显示的是已经通过审核的商户，可以设置开业状态，或者管理、例如设置手续费比例、是否开启分销等。</p><h3 data-line=\"6\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.43; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.5em;\"><a id=\"PC_6\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>商户PC端管理后台地址</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">见下图：<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/badcc924e72428558726450b4b9b0ed9_405x613.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><h2 data-line=\"9\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"_9\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>入驻审核</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">入住商审核，显示的是未通过审核的商户，可以对其进行审核。</p><h3 data-line=\"11\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.43; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.5em;\"><a id=\"_11\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>用户申请入驻流程</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">首先，我们在小程序设置-&gt;个人中心 菜单栏：添加“入驻商”菜单<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">用户即可在以下位置申请：<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/5c5b13f4975d2eaf33aa86af5739a0d2_398x716.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"></p><h2 data-line=\"16\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"_16\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>所售类目管理</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">所售类目管理，可以添加分类，那么入驻商入驻的时候，就可以选择其申请销售的类目。</p><h2 data-line=\"19\" class=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; padding: 0px 0px 0.3em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.225; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><a id=\"_19\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\"></a>提现管理</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px;\">入驻商卖出产品，并且订单已超过售后期后，货款会结算到其资产账号。商家可以对余额进行提现，提现申请后即会出现在“提现管理”列表，平台可以对提现进行操作。<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">若是微信提现，<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-weight: bolder;\">平台需开通微信支付企业付款到零钱功能</span>，具体请参考《小程序常用设置及参数获取》章节<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">登录微信支付商户平台：<a href=\"https://pay.weixin.qq.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(65, 131, 196); outline: 0px;\">https://pay.weixin.qq.com/</a><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://box.kancloud.cn/e9b73cdf872efdfbb2ce7826352129f5_516x313.png\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">申请开通“企业付款到零钱”。<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; display: block; margin: 0.2em;\">注意：根据微信最新要求，新申请商户号需要使用企业付款功能需同时满足以下两个条件：</p><ol style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 1.7em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 28px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-size-adjus